 1- (lmạdẖạ ạ̉sẖkwk lqlby wkạ̉nk mṣdr krby)2
 wạ̉lwmk ʿly̱ mạ ykdr ṣfw drby lmạdẖạ ạ̉sẖkwk lqlby
 wạ̉nt tḥzn lbkạỷy wạ̉nt tsrʿ lʿzạỷy (wạ̉nt nwr lẓlạmy wạ̉nt ldạỷy dwạỷy)2
 2- (lmạdẖạ ạ̉nsy̱ mạḍy wlmsạt ydk fy)2
