 lytk tgẖfr sẖkwạy wymlạ̉ nwrk ʿynạy (yạ mn ʿynạh lạ tgẖmḍ ạ̉w tgẖfl ʿn rw̉yạy)2
 3- (lhdẖạ ạ̉dʿwk bqlby fạ̉nt kẖạlqy wrby)2
 wʿlyk ạ̉lqy hmy yạ mn dẖqt ạlhm lạ̉jly lhdẖạ ạ̉dʿwk bqlby
 kl ạ̉mry fy ydyk wạlgẖd mḥfwẓ ldyk (ạ̉tẖq fy sẖkẖṣk wfy ḥbk yạ nạqsẖny ʿly̱ kfyk)2</lyrics>
